  tenManEn: The disappearance
  tenManVi: "V\u1EE5 m\u1EA5t t\xEDch"
  img: {fileID: 21300000, guid: fc0e9f6afe7d3824dbef49f91f83ce43, type: 3}
  objCauHoi: {fileID: -3307502091435878216, guid: 0192e41c3c347c8419bba1ecaf925cf0, type: 3}
  loai: 0
  motas:
  - yeuCau:
    - Recently there have been disappearances in this area. After investigating,
      the police realized that the most suspicious area was Dan's room. Look for
      anything unusual?
    - "D\u1EA1o g\u1EA7n \u0111\xE2y \u1EDF khu v\u1EF1c n\xE0y s\u1EA3y ra c\xE1c
      v\u1EE5 m\u1EA5t t\xEDch, sau khi \u0111i\u1EC1u tra th\xEC c\u1EA3nh s\xE1t
      nh\u1EADn ra r\u1EB1ng khu v\u1EF1c kh\u1EA3 nghi nh\u1EA5t l\xE0 c\u0103n
      ph\xF2ng c\u1EE7a Dan. H\xE3y t\xECm xem c\xF3 g\xEC b\u1EA5t th\u01B0\u1EDDng
      kh\xF4ng?"
    lyGiai:
    - There is someone in the closet, clearly this is the person who has gone missing.
    - "C\xF3 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi trong t\u1EE7 r\xF5 r\xE0ng \u0111\xE2y l\xE0 ng\u01B0\u1EDDi
      \u0111\xE3 b\u1ECB m\u1EA5t t\xEDch."
  - yeuCau:
    - It is very likely that the previous disappearances were also caused by Dan,
      is there any evidence?
    - "R\u1EA5t c\xF3 kh\u1EA3 n\u0103ng nh\u1EEFng v\u1EE5 m\u1EA5t t\xEDch tr\u01B0\u1EDBc
      \u0111\xF3 c\u0169ng do Dan g\xE2y ra, c\xF3 ch\u1EE9ng c\u1EE9 g\xEC kh\xF4ng?"
    lyGiai:
    - On this paper, the name of three people who have disappeared recently, there
      is also a brick in their names, which proves that previous disappearance cases
      are related to Dan.
    - "Tr\xEAn t\u1EDD gi\u1EA5y n\xE0y ghi t\xEAn ba ng\u01B0\u1EDDi \u0111\xE3
      m\u1EA5t t\xEDch g\u1EA7n \u0111\xE2y, c\xF2n c\xF3 v\u1EBFt g\u1EA1ch \u1EDF
      t\xEAn c\u1EE7a h\u1ECD \u0111i\u1EC1u n\xE0y ch\u1EE9ng t\u1ECF c\xE1c v\u1EE5
      m\u1EA5t t\xEDch tr\u01B0\u1EDBc \u0111\xF3 \u0111\u1EC1u li\xEAn quan \u0111\u1EBFn
      Dan."
  - yeuCau:
    - According to information from surrounding people, Dan rarely goes out, they
      only saw Dan go out before the disappearances happened. Is there anything that
      proves this is true?
    - "Theo nh\u01B0 th\xF4ng tin c\u1EE7a ng\u01B0\u1EDDi d\xE2n xung quanh th\xEC
      r\u1EA5t \xEDt khi Dan ra ngo\xE0i, h\u1ECD ch\u1EC9 th\u1EA5y Dan ra ngo\xE0i
      tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi c\xE1c v\u1EE5 m\u1EA5t t\xEDch x\u1EA3y ra. C\xF3 g\xEC
      ch\u1EE9ng minh \u0111i\u1EC1u n\xE0y \u0111\xFAng kh\xF4ng?"
    lyGiai:
    - Dan rarely goes out and the trash bags are still in the room.
    - "Dan r\u1EA5t \xEDt khi ra ngo\xE0i c\xE1c t\xFAi r\xE1c v\u1EABn c\xF2n trong
      ph\xF2ng."
  - yeuCau:
    - Before committing these crimes, Dan was an excellent student. Is there any
      proof?
    - "Tr\u01B0\u1EDBc khi g\xE2y ra c\xE1c v\u1EE5 \xE1n n\xE0y Dan t\u1EEBng l\xE0
      m\u1ED9t sinh vi\xEAn \u01B0u t\xFA. C\xF3 g\xEC ch\u1EE9ng minh kh\xF4ng?"
    lyGiai:
    - This certificate of merit is from Dan
    - "B\u1EB1ng khen n\xE0y c\u1EE7a Dan."
  - yeuCau:
    - Because of his excellence, Dan has many people's expectations, causing pressure
      leading to mental instability. This information correct?
    - "V\xEC s\u1EF1 xu\u1EA5t s\u1EAFc c\u1EE7a m\xECnh n\xEAn Dan \u0111\u01B0\u1EE3c
      nhi\u1EC1u ng\u01B0\u1EDDi k\u1EF3 v\u1ECDng, g\xE2y \xE1p l\u1EF1c d\u1EABn
      \u0111\u1EBFn tinh th\u1EA7n b\u1EA5t \u1ED5n. Th\xF4ng tin n\xE0y c\xF3 \u0111\xFAng
      kh\xF4ng?"
    lyGiai:
    - This potion must be a sedative.
    - "L\u1ECD thu\u1ED1c n\xE0y ch\u1EAFc h\u1EB3n l\xE0 thu\u1ED1c an th\u1EA7n."
